title: Ep 72: Eleanor Kerrigan Visits & It Gets REAL, YO
description: The hilarious Eleanor Kerrigan joins me and we discuss her childhood growing up among 10 siblings, her life at the Comedy Store, depression and the fear of becoming your parents. She's hilarious and honest and I know you will love her as much as I do. Enjoy!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
